>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
decimal to binary : (string form of binary number)
std::string binary = std::bitset<bitWidth>(N).to_string(); //to binary
Binary to decimal : (string form of binary number)
unsigned long decimal = std::bitset<bitWidth>("1001").to_ulong();

bitWidth : no of bits you want
